dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents forests for Wood County, Wisconsin at year-end 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Wood_Forests_YE2016.gdb. [This dataset shows the locations of the Wood County Forests.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://opendata.woodcogis.com/
